---
title: Roasted Cauliflower Burrito Rice Bowl with Corn Salsa, Avocado & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Try this twist on a burrito bowl, with spiced and roasted cauliflower, plus classic Mexican sides topping a generous serve of our aromatic garlic rice. It's the ideal recipe to try something new and taste just how versatile veggies can be!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cauliflower-burrito-bowl-015f0c0d.jpg
